data.description: SPACE TO GROW! Come HOME to this ADORABLE country cottage with a lot of livability. Located in Southside, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has had a TON of updates! Comfortable family room with kitchen combination will be perfect for you and your guest! EFFECIENT and inviting kitchen looks good against groceries with updated counters, stainless appliances, and refinished cabinets. NEED MORE SPACE? Lower level living area could also serves as a family sized recreation room for entertaining!  Primary bedroom and bath are situated for privacy with a walk in closet, garden tub and shower.  MEANT TO BE ENJOYED the backyard includes an above ground pool, spacious yard and screened in porch perfect for relaxing after a long day! PRECIOUS MEMORIES BEGIN HERE!
